caption:
He’s been out in the world all day—dealing with stress, pressure, and probably bad attitudes.
So I took two minutes to freshen up…
Because this is the peace he comes home to.
Not a hot mess. Not a cold shoulder.
A warm smile, soft touch, and the kind of love only a wife can give.
